gros]]\n{{col-3}}\n*[[Club Hidalguense|Hidalguense]]\n*[[Deportivo Independiente Mexiquense|Independiente Mexiquense]]\n*[[C.D. Matamoros|Matamoros]]\n*[[C.F. Pachuca|Pachuca]] *\n*[[Sk Sport Street Soccer]]\n*[[C.F. Texcoco|Texcoco]]\n*[[Uni\u00f3n Acolman]]\n*[[Universidad del F\u00fatbol]] \n{{col-end}}\n\n===Group VIII===\n(2019-2020) There are 15 teams in Group 8 (G8)\n{{col-start}}\n{{col-3}}\n*[[4D Morelia]] (franchise loan from [[Tigres Blancos Gestalt]])\n*[[Celaya F.C.|Celaya]] **\n*[[Cocodrilos de L\u00e1zaro C\u00e1rdenas]]\n*[[Delfines de Abasolo]]\n*[[Club Fundadores|Fundadores]]\n*[[Jaibos Cortazar F.C.]] (franchise registered as [[Deportivo Soria]])\n*[[C.F. La Piedad|La Piedad]] ***\n*[[Lobos ITECA]]\n{{col-3}}\n*[[Real Quer\u00e9taro]]\n*[[Sahuayo F.C.|Sahuayo]]\n*[[Salamanca F.C.|Salamanca]]\n*[[Tiburones Freseros F.C.|Tiburones Freseros]]\n*[[Titanes de Quer\u00e9taro]]\n*[[C.D. Yur\u00e9cuaro|Yur\u00e9cuaro]]\n*[[Zorros de Cadereyta]] (franchise loan from [[San Juan del R\u00edo F.C.|San Juan del R\u00edo]])\n{{col-end}}\n\n===Group IX===\n(2019-2020) There are 9 teams in Group 9 (G9)\n{{col-start}}\n{{col-3}}\n*[[Alacranes de Durango]] ***\n*[[Atl\u00e9tico Leon\u00e9s]]\n*[[Durazneros de Jerez]] (franchise loan from [[FC Zacatecas]])\n*[[Empresarios del Rinc\u00f3n F.C.|Empresarios del Rinc\u00f3n]] (franchise loan from [[Real Olmeca Sport]])\n*[[Mineros de Fresnillo F.C.|Mineros de Fresnillo]] ***\n{{col-3}}\n*[[Mineros de Zacatecas]] **\n*[[Somnus F.C.|Somnus]] (franchise loan from [[Real Magari]])\n*[[San Pancho F.C.]] (franchise loan from [[C.H. F\u00fatbol Club]])\n*[[Tuzos UAZ]] ***\n{{col-end}}\n\n===Group X===\n(2019-2020) There are 19 teams in Group 10 (G10) Note: [[Loros UdeC]] (dissolved on December 27, 2019; will not participate in Clausura 2020)\n{{col-start}}\n{{col-3}}\n*[[Acatl\u00e1n F.C.|Acatl\u00e1n]]\n*[[C.D. Ayense|Ayense]]\n*[[Catedr\u00e1ticos Elite F.C.|Catedr\u00e1ticos Elite]]\n*[[Deportivo CAFESSA Tlajomulco|CAFESSA]